Host Your Event at Nine State Brewery
Looking for the perfect venue for your next event? Look no further than Nine State Brewery!
Why Choose Nine State?
Prime Location:
Conveniently located in downtown Inverness.
Flexible Capacity:
Accommodates groups of 15-75 guests.
Customizable Options:
We're open to your ideas and suggestions to make planning easy.
Diverse Beverage Selection:
Enjoy a wide range of beers on tap, sangria, seltzer, wine, and non-alcoholic beverages.
Book With Ease:
Provide details in the event form and we will contact you to discuss details and schedule your event.
Entertainment Options:
We can suggest entertainment or you can bring your own.
Catering Flexibility:
Choose from our kitchen menu or we can customize according to your needs.
Note - We do not allow any outside drinks/beverages alcohol or non alcohol into our building.
Private Event Space:
Available Monday-Sunday, during our open hours or as a private rental.
Ready to Book?
Please fill out the event form.
